Head of Brokerage
Offshore Recruitment Services
UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Responsibilities:
•	Adopt trading strategies that effectively result in best execution, and minimum market impact
•	Co-ordinate closely with fund managers and clients in terms of price and time execution, implementation of trading strategies, reporting, in addition to any other related issues
•	Build excellent business relationships with the banks trading clients where appropriate including traders and sales traders to facilitate trade execution and settlement, or any other related business issues
•	Monitor and resolve any trading errors or any trading difficulty or any other related issues that could put the client or bank at risk
•	Obtain information from economists, analysts, and the market itself, plus own views to formulate and communicate an up to date view of the market
•	Develop and maintain databases to track trades (transaction records and confirmation), commissions, profits where necessary
•	Continue to grow the reputation and client base of the bank through business development.
•	Be able to improve the profitability of the unit and continuously looking to improve processes
•	Manage a team of Junior Brokers guiding them in their development.
REQUIREMENTS
Qualifications:
•Bachelor’s degree in related subject - Business/Finance/Economics
•Minimum of 7 years Equity trading experience ideally with a MENA/Emerging Markets focus
•Professionally qualified with appropriate SII &/or CFA qualifications is an advantage
•Highly motivated, self-assured with solid quantitative, and analytical skills, excellent communication skills good team player
•Must be Fluent in spoken and written Arabic and English
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Offshore Recruitment Services specialise in the recruitment of in all aspects of offshore vacancies for all levels of permanent, temporary and contract positions.
Whether a client is searching for a highly skilled candidate, looking to head hunt a specific individual, a team of contractors for a project or management of gifted personnel, we are ready and have a proven track record of meeting such requirements.
Offshore Recruitment Services was formed with the specific aim of providing a quality service to link key candidates to our clients. We find the right people for your business.
